OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with early patchy
OL,6,Fdrizzle possible. Then becoming dry
OL,7,Fand brighter for most places with some
OL,8,Fsunny intervals developing, but also
OL,9,Fperhaps isolated light coastal
OL,10,Fshowers. Light northerly winds inland,
OL,11,Fbreezy and cooler along the coast.
OL,12,FTemperatures close to average.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells and patchy
OL,15,Fcloud, with a chance of a few light
OL,16,Fshowers reaching coastal areas, where
OL,17,Fit will remain breezy. Becoming cooler
OL,18,Ffor many places, compared to recent
OL,19,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
