OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry with patchy cloud,
OL,6,Fespecially through the morning, but
OL,7,Falso sunny spells which will become
OL,8,Fprolonged later. Highest temperatures
OL,9,Finland, breezy and rather cool along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FLargely dry and often cloudy, but also
OL,14,Fsome sunny spells will occur. Staying
OL,15,Fpredominantly dry, but with a small
OL,16,Fchance of coastal showers Monday.
OL,17,FTemperatures generally average or
OL,18,Fslightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
